---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="contact"
  description="how to get in touch with mikael ristmets."
>
  <article class="container">
    <header class="page-head">
      <p class="eyebrow">§ &nbsp; contact</p>
      <h1>get in touch</h1>
      <hr class="rule rule--short" />
    </header>

    <div class="prose">
      <p class="lede">
        <span class="red">mina usun, et arhitektuur pole üksnes ruumikujundamise
        tööriist, vaid ka ühiskonna, misläbi on võimalik luua paremat
        elu kõigile.</span>
      </p>
      <p class="lede">
        <span class="blue">architecture is not just something we use to design
        the space around us, but something that also shapes society,
        which allows for the creation of better lives for everyone.</span>
      </p>

      <ul class="links">
        <li><a href="mailto:mikael.ristmets@gmail.com">mikael.ristmets@gmail.com</a></li>
        <li><a href="tel:+3725181279">+372 518 1279</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/" rel="me noopener" target="_blank">linkedin</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://soundcloud.com/mikzor" rel="me noopener" target="_blank">soundcloud</a></li>
        <li><a href="/feed.xml">rss</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-head {
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-6);
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--sp-3);
    max-width: var(--measure);
  }
  .page-head h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-grotesk);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: var(--fs-3xl);
    line-height: var(--lh-tight);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-display);
  }
  .lede {
    font-family: var(--font-grotesk);
    font-size: var(--fs-md);
    line-height: 1.4;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
  }
  .links {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-top: var(--sp-5);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--sp-2);
  }
  .links li::before {
    content: '→';
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-right: var(--sp-2);
  }
</style>
